div.bibl: Svenska Kuriren, Dec. 25, 1913. BALDER LODGE NO. 12, I. O. S.

body.p: The Balder Lodge No. 12, I. O. S., has elected the following officers: Grand Master: August Lindeberg; vice-Grand Master: Andrew Linden; recording secretary: Ernst Ancharstrand; financial secretary: Charles E. Carlson; treasurer: Alfred Anderson; chief: F. G. E. Cedervall; secretary to the trustees: Gust Olson; examning Doctor: Emil Nels Larson. Charles E. Carlson and Gust Olson were elected delegates to the Grand Lodge.
